---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="CatPlay — Coming Soon" description="An iOS app for understanding your cat's behavior. Join the waitlist.">
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow">Coming soon · iOS</span>
      <h1>CatPlay</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        Notice patterns. Spot changes. Understand your cat better — without becoming a cat behaviorist.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          CatPlay is a small iOS app that helps you keep track of the things that matter — play sessions, eating habits, litter box patterns, weight, mood. Not as a chore, but as a way to actually <em>see</em> your cat's life clearly enough to notice when something changes.
        </p>

        <p>
          It's built by the same people who write paw and sage, with the same belief: paying attention is the foundation of good care.
        </p>

        <h2>What's coming</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Multi-cat profiles with personality tracking</li>
          <li>A weekly "report card" you can share</li>
          <li>Pattern detection for behavior, eating, and health signals</li>
          <li>Reminders that don't feel like guilt</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="waitlist-box">
        <span class="eyebrow">Get early access</span>
        <h3>Join the waitlist.</h3>
        <p>Be the first to know when CatPlay launches. Early access, founding-member pricing, and a free month for everyone on the list.</p>
        <form action="https://YOUR-MAILERLITE-FORM-URL" method="post" class="email-form">
          <input
            type="email"
            name="email"
            placeholder="your@email.com"
            required
            aria-label="Email address"
          />
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-accent">Join waitlist</button>
        </form>
        <p class="fineprint">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header { padding: 5rem 0 2rem; text-align: center; }
  .page-header .eyebrow { display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .lede {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 1.5rem auto 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .content-section { padding: 2rem 0 5rem; }
  .prose { font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 3rem; }

  .waitlist-box {
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--sage-50) 0%, var(--cream-200) 100%);
    border: 1px solid var(--sage-300);
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .waitlist-box .eyebrow { display: block; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .waitlist-box h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }
  .waitlist-box p {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  .email-form {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto 0.75rem;
  }
  .email-form input {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: var(--cream-100);
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .email-form input:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--sage-700);
  }
  .fineprint {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .email-form { flex-direction: column; }
  }
</style>
